From d589bc5b598abbb6f384f292ba5111c06af7b604 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <ptarjan@gmail.com>
Date: Sat, 4 Jul 2026 20:38:19 -0600
Subject: [PATCH] New: Gamarr application support

Adds Gamarr (https://github.com/gamarr-app/Gamarr) as an application
type so Prowlarr can sync indexers to it. Gamarr is a Radarr fork for
game libraries; its indexer API is contract-compatible with Radarr v3
(/api/v3/indexer with Newznab/Torznab implementations), so this follows
the existing Whisparr/Radarr application pattern with game-appropriate
default sync categories (Console 1000s, PC 4000s).
